import React from 'react'; import Card from 'react-bootstrap/Card'; import ListGroup from 'react-bootstrap/ListGroup'; import data from '../components/packet.json' const About = () => { return (
{data.map((item) => ( {item.name} Energy{item.energy_value} {item.energy_unit} Protein{item.proteins_value} {item.proteins_unit} Carbohydrates: {item.carbohydrates_value}{" "} {item.carbohydrates_unit} Fat:{item.fat_value} {item.fat_unit}{" "} Card Link Another Link ))}
) } export default About; {item.name} Some quick example text to build on the card title and make up the bulk of the card's content. Cras justo odio Dapibus ac facilisis in Vestibulum at eros Card Link Another Link
